Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.73,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉帶我去洗溫泉 當做是情人節的回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到大家的溫柔對待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我度過了一個溫暖快樂的幸福時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人雀躍不已的新學期開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.89,0:01:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也都升為二年級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.93,0:01:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的新生都很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.73,0:01:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾跟小魚也來參加開學典禮就好了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是花粉的過敏就夠受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.81,0:02:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪還受得了一直待在那裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那王子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是開學典禮的幹部 好像很忙的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.58,0:02:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很快就會受到一年級新生愛的攻勢了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.39,0:02:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長…我的學生手冊好像弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事問我也沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沒有辦法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得在哪裡弄丟的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.43,0:02:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳先告訴我妳的姓名與班級吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.54,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有森佐登美 15歲 天蠍座 B型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡手工藝 魅力在修長的腳踝..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是園宮里奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家都說我像藤原靜香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你個頭啦 白癡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家羨慕的這一關 你衝得過去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.99,0:02:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年也許還會成為學生會長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希好像不太喜歡這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.73,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我還在家長席上接收到疑似紫吳的電波呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 他有來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一年級裡有草摩家的人入學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.51,0:03:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說他們就像我的弟弟一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定得出席一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.71,0:03:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他們光鮮亮麗的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊？用那種懷疑的眼神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是認為我是打女高中生的主意才去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真討厭耶 這群失去天真浪漫的小傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有草摩家的人要入學呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的人？男的還是女的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男的 而且是兩位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？那去見他們一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 身為學長總得教一下學弟才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如這個學校的規矩、開溜之道等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你去帶他們過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 去帶他們來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我 叫她去就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.56,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種麻煩事幹嘛非叫小透去才行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.87,0:04:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我本來就打算去跟他們打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但難得嘛 阿夾要不要也一起去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 為什麼在學校還得見這些傢伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校見面搞不好感覺又不一樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許別有一番滋味唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像愈來愈不能抗拒小透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.74,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉跟潑春是哪一班的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.68,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠了 妳在這裡等 我去問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？真的嗎？不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.65,0:05:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妳們知道有兩個叫做草摩的白髮跟金髮的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道 就在我們班上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他們過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 至少也搞清楚班級嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼總是迷迷糊糊的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩挺可愛的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是挺可愛的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是看起來有點呆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會反抗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個性強的女孩那才受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看來好像還挺聽話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.15,0:05:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕 可怕 好可怕喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看吧 就是迷迷糊糊的才會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的時候罩子要放亮點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是這樣子 就算被綁架了也怪不了誰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.21,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說一個人的時候啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在身邊的時候迷糊點是沒有關係的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有別的意思喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別誤會喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是想歪了 那可就頭大了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？別的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在說什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是豬頭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不好穿 哪有人穿女生制服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.18,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屌兒啷當的潑春還好一點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係 蠻速配的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很速配吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 你這什麼打扮呀 紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.81,0:07:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 工作結束了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處巡視一下 順道過來看看他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家叫我在學校不要太出風頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要是太出風頭的話就會受到女生的攻擊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定在學校要酷一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酷嗎？這種樣子會酷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得好 2年D班的草摩夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那個橘子頭也是很讓人不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.77,0:07:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生卻穿女生制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是空前絕後的厚顏無恥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算老師允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也絕不原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是這裡的學生會長 竹井誠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有另一個頭銜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是學校防衛隊的隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又多了個白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才開學就是一堆問題學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先你這算什麼 草摩潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我剝掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴著滿頭白假髮到處亂逛 你也太囂張了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會長 他這是真的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 由希～ 真是太美了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,言歸正傳 真髮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是下面的是黑的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這是真髮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思議了 怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.08,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋 總不能說是牛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你這打扮算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你也是與生俱來的嗎？草摩紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.85,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒有男性的尊嚴嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就這樣 我看你這輩子也不會有出息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是 這樣比較適合我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要太嚴厲的責罵他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒責罵他喔 本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是基於常識在發表理所當然的言論而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少在那邊裝老大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在很刺耳耶 你這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我倒是想問你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰說襪子折三次就是乖寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒穿耳洞就不會被欺負嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮不是黑的難道就犯法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.86,0:09:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你是誰啊？是神明嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"黑色降臨"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你還真行呢 神明 說句話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫叫看呀 再囉唆呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 別欺負外行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆！白痴貓 你不要插嘴！白痴貓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我白痴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要揍人了喔 臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你跩什麼跩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次打架時 是誰夾著尾巴逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你自己不打的還說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底是那一邊的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊都一樣 豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 要來顆糖嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.89,0:09:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別找碴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算像紅葉這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不覺得他在學校也不錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正他遲早也會長大成人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要當男人 到那時候也不遲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會變得很帥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是想像紅葉變成男人的樣子 不是也挺有意思的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.04,0:09:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別被他洗腦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是適合本人的打扮最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是任性妄為 對其他的學生也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也太失禮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果由希也穿女生制服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春 如果你不適可而止 我就跟你絕交了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說錯話了 不可以生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.83,0:10:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別亂想！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不知不覺的就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個難纏的對手嘛 草摩潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.20,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你能證明你那頭亂髮是真髮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據確鑿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界還真是無奇不有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給他看了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給他看了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天算是我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.27,0:11:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但下次可沒這麼簡單喔 我會把你們一網打盡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人到底是來幹嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.92,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春 你在廁所是怎麼證明你的頭髮給他看的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行呀 妳要不要也和我試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}有沒有洗手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一但變黑誰也拿他沒辦法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 小透別放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}驀然地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得好累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真的累了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鐘響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得回教室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去時要不要去見見我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我想見見小透的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚點我再來接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟由希、阿夾講 你們可以等一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.40,0:12:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回教室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會 沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是無聊事 我會扁人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛真是大騷動一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果以後每天都這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕由希跟阿夾都會很傷腦筋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很快樂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.98,0:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說慊人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.18,0:13:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剛剛在開學典禮時聽紫吳說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是慊人自己突然說要來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.15,0:13:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想他會比大家晚點到學校來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想先告訴你們一聲比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕你們不想見到他 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是慊人…先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 本田透小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是慊人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會來學校？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子的見面方式可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一大跳 他好年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.84,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且好漂亮 一點都不輸給由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有他的眼神和波鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很淑女 也挺溫柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來人蠻不錯的 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是妳很可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你過獎了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在本家時沒能與妳打招呼 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是很怕生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是否生氣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.95,0:15:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那我再次自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.62,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是草摩家的大當家 慊人 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也是…請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.52,0:15:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像中的還平易近人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望今後能和妳成為好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也請妳多多關照由希他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想你喔 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.89,0:15:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好久沒見到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成熟了耶 也長高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對小透做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是打聲招呼而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對 小透 只是打聲招呼而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.22,0:16:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是由希 有件事情我一定要問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.99,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼過年時你沒出席宴會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼做這種事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近我對你也蠻寬大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.47,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你這樣做實在太傷我的心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.21,0:16:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我得再次教育你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那間你專用的房間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是草摩的大當家呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.94,0:17:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為違背大當家會沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不回教室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會挨罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 再不回紫吳那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他們也會擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.31,0:17:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 希望你有個愉快的高中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.51,0:17:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若最近你願意來找我 我會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打斷他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希非常的害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人真的沒對妳說什麼奇怪的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 真的只是打招呼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 我們去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天學校比較早結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小魚他們說好了要去輕鬆一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正難得嘛 大家一起去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.81,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓由希受到慊人影響的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠快活起來罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這件事情而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.09,0:19:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀、石頭、布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要拖我下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是羽毛球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男人就別囉哩叭嗦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還帶著口罩打呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也可以不要打呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分組之後呢？遊戲規則呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼規則啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛球不需要規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用盡全力把球打出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力回打就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.45,0:19:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先倒的就是輸家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不錯 簡單明瞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太簡單明瞭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.33,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很囉唆耶 快到自己的陣地去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陣地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是陣營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 王子 好好修理那個橘子頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼 太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說小透…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是個醜八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在回程的車上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.69,0:20:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個醜八怪 真爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來又不怎麼聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是這種程度的女人的話 我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想由希也撐不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.97,0:20:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗我的人是不會得到幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希現在見到我還是會害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示他還沒忘記我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長期以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神上受到那樣的虐待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少也有一些無法忘掉的傷痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是慊人不會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人的人也會受到傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.70,0:20:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份創傷在他們之間永遠存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記傷痛需要很大的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.37,0:21:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢 小透又很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人長的很甜美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.75,0:21:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話由你說來感覺有點犯罪的意味喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很想得到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,描繪在內心的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱我的雙親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以回去的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家可以盡情歡笑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.67,0:21:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會被大家拋棄的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的歸屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫馨的一群人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.29,0:21:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來真的存在
